 Express like its counterpart in the UK. The name change still brings with it an abundance of tasty dishes that ev', '', '', '1450113197', '1402474112'), ('41', '1', '1', 'Shanghai International Film Festival (SIFF) Highlights', '', 'arts, family, shanghai international film festival', 'The Shanghai International Film Festival (SIFF) runs from June 14-22 and features over 300 films. Here are some of the top family friendly options.', '', '', '1450113197', '1402474800'), ('42', '1', '1', 'Win! Pizza Express voucher for RMB500', '', 'giveaway, win, pizza_express', 'Pizza Express is giving away a RMB500 voucher to one lucky winner. To win, please send the answer to the following question to ufwin@urbanatomy.com before June 18 with the subject \'Pizza Express\':  Q) What is your favorite pizza topping?', '', '', '1450113197', '1402475550'), ('43', '1', '1', 'Celebrate Dad', '', 'fathersday, holiday, special_events, father, dad', 'Don\'t forget this Sunday, June 15 is Father\'s Day. To celebrate, we\'ve compiled a list of all the ways you can treat Dad on his special day in Shanghai.', '', '', '1450113197', '1402478008'), ('44', '1', '1', 'Best in Show 2014 Winners', '', 'art, student, artwork, international_school, Shanghai', 'As part of the Urban Family arts-themed issue, we made an open call for student artwork submissions from the Shanghai international school community for a judged competition. We were overwhelmed by the response. We received 110 works from seven different', '', '', '1450113197', '1403075833'), ('45', '1', '1', 'Langham Hotel \'Angels\' Eyes\' Painting Competition', '', 'langham, student, artwork', 'On, Friday, June 13, students and teachers from the Luwan Special Needs Education School gathered at the Shanghai Langham Hotel at Xintiandi to participate in the official Angels’ Eyes painting competition. Fifteen students from this award-winning school', '', '', '1450113197', '1402898126'), ('46', '1', '1', 'Best in Show 2014 Submissions', '', 'student, artwork, international_schoools, colorbox', 'As part of the&nbsp;<em>Urban Family&nbsp;</em>arts-themed issue, we made an open call for student artwork submissions from the Shanghai international school community for a judged competition. Here is slideshow of a selection of submissions.', '', '', '1450113197', '1402911345'), ('47', '1', '1', 'Green City Mini World Cup', '', 'Mini_World_cup, green_city, Shanghai, soccer, footbal', 'Shanghai\'s Mini World Cup hosted by Green City and Urbanatomy Media kicked off over the weekend, June 14-15 in Jinqiao. The teams played through the heat while the kids had fun in the bouncy castles. A big thank you to all of the sponsors.', '', '', '1450113197', '1403504950'), ('48', '1', '1', 'East West Theatre\'s The Learned Ladies', '', 'East_West_Theatre, Learned_Ladies, theater, shanghai', 'Shanghai’s original English-language company, East West Theatre, returns to the stage this week. David Johansson (Almost, Maine) directs an adaptation of Moliere’s The Learned Ladies from June 18 to 23 at The Pearl. An outrageous farce, it follows young H', '', '', '1450113197', '1403068574'), ('49', '1', '1', 'Art supplies: The essential guide to help kids get creative at home', '', 'art, supplis, materials,', 'Most times, basics items - along with recycled objects and a few specialty materials - are all one needs for successful art making.', '', '', '1450113197', '1403071895'), ('50', '1', '1', 'Art classes: Disocver your inner Picasso', '', 'art, classes, children', '“It took me four years to paint like Raphael, but a lifetime to paint like a child.” --Pablo Picasso', '', '', '1450113197', '1403072588'), ('51', '1', '1', 'Win! Painting class at Paintertainment Shanghai', '', 'art, classes, children, kids, activities', 'Urban Family\'s weekly giveaway.', '', '', '1450113197', '1403074809'), ('52', '1', '1', 'Fete de la Musique', '', 'fete_de_la_musique, shanghai, music, family_friendly_festival', 'Shanghai\'s going to be in a musical mood when this worldwide celebration of music returns to the city for the fifth straight year. Expect plenty of free concerts and music performances, from Pudong to Songjiang, from large outdoor public spaces to intimat', '', '', '1450113197', '1403081433'), ('53', '1', '1', 'Day Trip: Thames Town, Sonjiang', '', 'Thames Town, Sonjiang, daytrip, travel , activity, features', 'The Urban Family guide to Thames Town', '', '', '1450113197', '1403689029'), ('54', '1', '1', 'The summer slide: Keeping young minds active this vacation', '', 'learning', 'Students of all ages digress two to three months in their academic skills during the summer if they do not have intellectual stimulation', '', '', '1450113197', '1403249561'), ('55', '1', '1', 'Shanghai\'s Best Art Museums', '', 'arts, learning, museums, activities', 'The city’s art scene is booming making this the perfect time explore the multitude of museums, sculptures and galleries around town.', '', '', '1450113197', '1403688622'), ('56', '1', '1', 'BISS Head of Music on Tour with Anuna', '', 'BISS, Pudong, Shanghai, school_news', '“It’s like a surrealistic dream come true… kind of like a guitar player getting into The Beatles!” That’s how Russell Seaton, British International School Shanghai (BISS) Pudong’s Head of Music, describes embarking on the China tour with world-renowned Ce', '', '', '1450113197', '1403251813'), ('57', '1', '1', 'Walk on the wild side: Moganshan Lu art district', '', 'arts, moganshan lu, galleries, activities', 'For the edgier side of the Shanghai contemporary art scene, you won’t want to miss the Moganshan Lu area of the Putuo District.', '', '', '1450113197', '1403502697'), ('58', '1', '1', 'Al fresco dining:  Sit in the sun all summer long', '', 'eat-drink', 'It might be hot, but on those days when you long to be outside with the kids, head to one of these restaurants for a cool drink and light fare', '', '', '1450113197', '1403503291'), ('59', '1', '1', 'Fight the bite: Keep mosquitoes at bay with 