ure Square Kids Fair is taking place for the third time, this time sponsored by Sung Hong Kai Properties Reading Club. Following the theme “Let’s Play Together!”, the fair takes advantage of Shanghai Culture Squar', '', '', '1450113207', '1432105580'), ('210', '1', '1', 'Wellington College 1 Year!', '', 'Wellington, College, Students, Parents, Games, Cricket, Anniversary, Shanghai', 'Shanghai\'s only school cricket pitch saw over 800 of the Wellington Community celebrating the end of the College\'s first year last weekend. The Summer Fayre was filled with student- and parent organized games and activities, and a handful of Shanghai\'s lo', '', '', '1450113207', '1433398722'), ('211', '1', '1', 'Take it Outside!', '', 'Activities, Shanghai, Kids, Outdoors, Nature, Summer, Beach, Parks', 'Summer is here and we should all be outside enjoying the beautiful weather before it gets too hot. Kids need to have some nature experiences and even if you live in Shanghai it is possible to have some outdoorsy fun!', '', '', '1450113207', '1432289128'), ('212', '1', '1', 'Mom Blogger: Taking My Fitness to the next Level', '', 'Mom Blogger, Fitness, Kids, Family, Fitness 443, Gym, Exercise, Health', 'When you’re a mom sometimes you forget to do things for yourself. Your days are filled with getting kids dressed, taking kids to school, doing grocery shopping to make sure the kids have enough of whatever they’ve decided to only eat this week, picking up', '', '', '1450113207', '1432547526'), ('213', '1', '1', 'Forever Young @ Renaissance Shanghai Pudong Hotel', '', 'Children\'s Day, Renaissance Hotel, Pudong, Cooking, Buffet, Competition, Events, Entertainment', 'Everyone still has an inner child and what better way to enjoy your youth and a day with your kids than with the Children’s Day Buffet at the Renaissance Shanghai Pudong Hotel’s Brassiere.', '', '', '1450113207', '1432610134'), ('214', '1', '1', 'Celebrate Children\'s Day at 10 Corso Como this weekend!', '', 'China, Shanghai,