al—and not just because it’s a fairy tale. As a cast member, it’s amazing how quickly the five months of rehearsal whirl by.', '', '', '1450113207', '1433385977'), ('220', '1', '1', 'Grand Opening of EIC Yangpu Campus', '', 'EIC, New Pathway, Yangpu, Campus, university, Wanda Plaza, Student, Learning', 'With already 4 campuses at People Square, Xujiahui, Gubei and Pudong in Shanghai, EIC Group is happy to announce a new campus opening on May 29, 2015 in Yangpu District.', '', '', '1450113207', '1433472262'), ('221', '1', '1', 'Recipe: Spanish Tomato and Strawberry Gazpacho', '', 'Recipe, Gazpacho, Tomato, Strawberry, Renaissance, Yangtze, Hotel, Cooking Class, Urban Family', 'A few weeks ago, Urban Family hosted a fun cooking class at Raphael\'s at Shanghai Renaissance Yangtze Hotel. Here is one of the recipes the ten families got to try out under the direction of chef Alejandro Pico Bellas. This cold tomato and strawberry soup', '', '', '1450113207', '1433740419'), ('222', '1', '1', 'Father’s Day at Le Royal Meridien', '', 'Father\'s Day, Le Royal Meridien, Eat & Drink, Food, Restaurant, Hotel, Celebration, Dad', 'Dads get their day of celebration in June, and it’s the perfect opportunity to reach out and tell him how much he means to you. Whether he loves fine French cuisine, traditional Italian tastes or Cantonese delicacies, Le Royal Méridien Shanghai can offer', '', '', '1450113207', '1433902497'), ('223', '1', '1', 'June - July Issue Out Now - Download Here!', '', 'June, July, Issue, Out Now, Pets, Adoption, Print, Urban Family, Magazine', 'The June/July issue of Urban Family is out now – paper-and-ink-form citywide, digital pdf-form right here or in your browser here.', '', '', '1450113207', '1433917479'), ('224', '1', '1', 'Behind the Scenes of an Animal Adoption Event with YCIS Student Reiren', '', 'Adoption, Pets, Volunteering, YCIS, Fostering, Reiren, Bow Meow, Shanghai, Event', 'Reiren, a Year 12 student at Yew Chung International School of Shanghai (YCIS) has recently been using her language skills to help animals and families in Shanghai. Since last October, she has been volunteering at a local Japanese animal organization call', '', '', '1450113207', '1433990770'), ('225', '1', '1', 'Father\'s Day Gifts: DIY Photo Message', '', 'Father\'s Day, Gift, Present, DIY, Photography, Crafts, Dad, Kids, Shanghai', 'Father’s Day is on June 21 and it’s about time to start thinking about gifts. Living in Shanghai, this part can be difficult because more stuff is often the last thing families need!', '', '', '1450113207', '1434335379'), ('226', '1', '1', 'Shanghai by Bike - WeeRide', '', 'WeeRide, Bike, Bicycle, Shanghai, kids, Co-Pilot, Transportation', 'Shanghai is a city best seen by bicycle according to many. Without the crowds of people, careless taxi drivers and traffic congestion, riding a bicycle has many pros.', '', '', '1450113207', '1434345165'), ('227', '1', '1', 'Mom Blogger: The Thing I look Forward To Most', '', 'Mom Blogger, Nicole Chia, Summer, Vacation, Canada, Home, Single Mom, Food, Travel, Kids', 'Summer brings a lot of excitement to Shanghai. Whether you’re leaving for good, have a child who’s graduating school, or getting ready for a summer vacation; this time of year is all about chaotic last minute lunch dates and trips to the fake market (agai', '', '', '1450113207', '1434421342'), ('228', '1', '1', 'Thank You Dad for Everything!', '', 'Father\'s Day, Golden Sunday, InterContinental, Hotel, Brunch, Promotions, Food, Beer, Family', 'Give your dad the best Father’s Day present by taking him to the Golden Sunday brunch at the InterContinental Hotel.', '', '', '1450113207', '1434429075');
