ing families with children aged 3-12 years old interested in Awesome Summer Camp to a guided tour of the facilities including a mini summer camp trial session to gain an insight into a day', '', '', '1450113207', '1435198474'), ('235', '1', '1', 'What a Show at Wellington College!', '', 'Pippin, Wellington, College, Theatre, Show, Performance, Michael Larsen-Disney', 'Wellington held its first major musical production in the College Theatre on 18th, 19th and 20th June, performing the Tony Award-winning musical, \'Pippin\': one young man’s quest to become extraordinary.', '', '', '1450113207', '1435284398'), ('236', '1', '1', 'Weekend Event Roundup', '', 'Events, Weekend, Shanghai, Family, Fun, Let\'s Brick, Paulaner, Wet Party, Grand Hyatt, Cooking Class, Soccer School', 'Don\'t miss out on any of the family fun Shanghai offers! Here are our picks for this weekend\'s events:', '', '', '1450113207', '1435293650'), ('237', '1', '1', 'Dulwich Students Building an Orphanage in Uganda', '', 'Dulwich, College, Volunteering, Summer, Students, Bukinda, Uganda, Orphanage, Courtney McAtee', 'A team of students and teachers from Dulwich College Shanghai are working alongside Peace and Golden Magezi in Bukinda, Uganda, in order to build, support and run an orphanage that will give 40 kids some hope of love, family and education for the future.', '', '', '1450113207', '1435555547'), ('238', '1', '1', 'AKSIL Teams Enjoy Huge Success in Shanghai’s SIYSL 2014/15 Soccer League', '', 'AKSIL, Active Kidz, Shanghai, Sports, soccer, SIYSL, tournament, competition, coach, kids, players', 'Teams from AKSIL (Active Kidz Shanghai International League) were hugely successful in the Shanghai International Youth Soccer League (SIYSL) 2014/15, picking up the championship prizes in the Division 1 competition for years U10, U12 and U14.  AKSIL team', '', '', '1450113207', '1435717823'), ('239', '1', '1', 'Family Events of the Week Roundup', '', 'Events, Shanghai, Family, stepping stones, dragon a